{"tid":881939,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓價回調】嘉湖551呎3房快穿「5球」 呎價僅9147元","createTime":"2018-10-29T23:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T01:21:04.000Z","uid":147097,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ca8c963ee441608d837fac2c0ad598f4f8931779","tid":881939,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"天水圍嘉湖山莊樓價明顯回落，2房頻見「4字頭」成交外，3房單位亦快將跌穿「5字頭」。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產分行經理林家倫指，嘉湖山莊樂湖居 11座低層C室，實用面積551平方呎3房，業主早於本月中以550萬放售，單位仍有租約，雖未能睇樓，最終外區買家在大幅減價下決定「無樓睇」情況下連租約入市，造價504萬，減價46萬或8.4%，呎價僅9,147元。"},{"pid":"3d460723c6568008cdc0cb3e789263effce2baff","tid":881939,"uid":16061,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:44:25.000Z","msg":"嘉湖返去千幾蚊尺就合理水平喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d6dca1fe65d567d838e85b7953dc671061dc30","tid":881939,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:48:01.000Z","msg":"林太呎價幾多<br />\n應該仲賺緊喎"},{"pid":"032062838b0e42c961cc0ff2ec59325c4b2ffad2","tid":881939,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:52:55.000Z","msg":"減咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e92a8db4080a872802a665022e7a359aba8962c","tid":881939,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:54:44.000Z","msg":"天水圍呢啲紅區<br />\n唔計"},{"pid":"a01e195b9fcdc3e6045aea7bbaac8325536616ac","tid":881939,"uid":77626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:56:56.000Z","msg":"班專家"},{"pid":"257e9ccc25058bce619c9e8bbd2cc8a97268050c","tid":881939,"uid":147097,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97d6dca1fe65d567d838e85b7953dc671061dc30","tid":881939,"uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:48:01.000Z","msg":"林太呎價幾多<br />\n應該仲賺緊喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"林太330買 係賺緊 仲賺埋住<br />\n<br />\n就過三年可以放埋tim<br />\n<br />